00:33:41.180 --> 00:33:44.180
When you look at the future,
there's a lot of uncertainty

00:33:44.180 --> 00:33:45.740
involved with it.

00:33:45.740 --> 00:33:48.080
One of the ways is dealing
with uncertainty.

00:33:48.080 --> 00:33:50.670
And probably the only scientific
way of dealing with

00:33:50.670 --> 00:33:53.180
uncertainty is through
the mechanism

00:33:53.180 --> 00:33:56.660
of probability models.

00:33:56.660 --> 00:34:01.760
So anything you want to deal
with, which is important,

00:34:01.760 --> 00:34:04.000
